title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS TOYOTA LANDCRUISER 200 SERIES – FUEL MANAGER PRE-FILTER KIT

content.rendered:
WESTERN FILTERS TOYOTA LANDCRUISER 200 SERIES – FUEL MANAGER PRE-FILTER KIT

Western Filters Toyota Landcruiser 200 Series Fuel Manager Pre-filter Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Fuel Manager Pre-Filter Water Separator Kit with WF Filter Removal Tool suits:

  • Toyota Landcruiser 200 Series 2008-on4.5L VDJ200 Turbo Diesel

This Filter unit is to be used as a Pre-Filter to separate water and contaminates thus avoiding costly repairs due to poor fuel quality. This kit includes very detailed fitting instructions and everything you will need & even where to fit it!

OS-21-FM Pre-Filter Kit includes:

  • 1x Fuel Filtration Unit Fuel Manager (Filters down to 30 Microns!)
  • Mounting Bolts, washers & nuts
  • Quality Fuel hose
  • Specially Designed Filter Mounting Bracket
  • Straight fittings
  • Blanking Plugs
  • Hose Clamps
  • Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)
  • Fittings to suit
  • WF Filter Removal Tool
  • 1x Instruction Sheet

To check out the full range of products available for your Landcruiser, CLICK HERE!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
